summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Water Department authorizing the sale and conveyance by Quit Claim Deeds (marked Exhibits "A" and "B") of a portion of real property commonly known as the Lake Youngs Aqueduct Right-of-Way (LYA R/W) located in Section 18, Township 22 North, Range 6 East, W.M., King County, Washington, to Delmar L.
